| *\[\[*id\]\]* | the Resource ID of the page (set by MODx when the page is created. | Often used in conjunction with the link syntax, e.g. {{&lt;a href=&quot;\[\[~\[\[*id\]\]\]\]&quot;&gt;Bookmark this page\!&lt;/a&gt;}} |
