| *\[\[*introtext\]\]* | the Introductory Text field (a.k.a. the summary). | Often used by Snippets to summarize posts, e.g. [ADDON:Ditto] {{&lt;div id=&quot;summary&quot;&gt;\[\[*introtext\]\]&lt;/div&gt;}} |
