| *\[\[*introtext\]\]* | the Introductory Text field (a.k.a. the summary). | _Often used by Snippets to summarize posts, e.g._ _[ADDON:Ditto]_ {{&lt;div id=&quot;summary&quot;&gt;\[\[*introtext\]\]&lt;/div&gt;}} |
| *\[\[*parent\]\]* | the ID of the parent page (if any). Set by MODx when the page is created. Can be altered by the user. | _Often used in conjunction with the \[\[~link\]\] syntax, e.g._ {{&lt;a href=&quot;\[\[~\[\[*parent\]\]\]\]&quot;&gt;Up to parent page&lt;/a&gt;}} |
